9/7/16.
Paraded in full marching order at 8 A.M. Marched all the morning covered some 9 miles. We have halted at a billet near Merrio and we march on again tomorrow. Whither we are bound I know not.
10/7/16.
Did not get our blankets last night, the transport that is carrying them has moved on; but it was warm enough in the straw of the barn. Rested here all day waiting for the order to move. It will come some time tonight I suppose. Marched off at 11.P.M. 
11/7/16.
